## Protocol

- Phases are ordered. Complete Phase N before Phase N+1 unless a WO explicitly spans phases.
- Within a phase, WOs are ordered by dependencies. Complete dependencies before dependents.
- **When a WO completes:** (1) Mark its Status `Complete` in this plan's table, (2) Move it to WO-INDEX Completed table, (3) Set **Next** to the next pending WO.
- DEVELOPMENT-PLAN, WO-INDEX, and WO-*.md files must stay aligned. The `validate-development-plan-alignment` gate runs at wo_exit and full_audit and fails if there is drift.
- If the plan changes (user request, discovery), update this document and WO-INDEX together.
